Current Position:  Blockchain Consultant, KPMG India 
Kartikey has a total of 5 years of development experience in Hyperledger.
He is currently working for KPMG India where he is involved in framing blockchain risk matrices and conducting risk analysis for different DLT-based platforms.
In his recent assessments, he has worked with the central bank in the Caribbean region to identify risks in CBDC they issued, conducted risk analysis for a stablecoin in production also conducted risk assessments for several smart contracts in production. 
In his early career, he was involved in building a BAAS(Blockchain as a service ) solution and also organized and participated in several recognized Hackathons.  
A technology-driven person who is always interested in learning and contributing to society.
